            "text": "Thanku induscraft for bringing my imagination into reality .\nBeing a marwari it's mandatory to enjoy food   with family, sitting on the floor, having one big thaal with lots and lots of dishes . But as our elders are aging it's difficult to sit on the floor and this makes a Little difference in our joy.\nSo u make an incredible dining set and hold the family together.\nThanku induscraft",
